[h3 
	" Stage by stage comments
	$LF
]h3
[h4 
	" Stage 1
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Just heavily optimized, abused bouncing of edges. Plus more entertainment, staying on that block was quite a challenge.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" Stage 2
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"More efficient way to go to the first turn. Minimized speed drops the the section with the moving platforms. And a more time save on the last turn.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" Stage 3
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Less speed lost when getting back on the stage, also better direction. Abused bouncing on the last segment.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" Stage 4
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"A lot of time was saved here from not going to far away from the goal when doing the skip. Also landing after the skip should be good positioned.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" Stage 5
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Hopping over the pit required an acceleration interupt, improved some time doing it on the right frame. Also more efficient way taking the turns. And the last pit was also done as effient as possible by using an acceleration interupt.
	$LF
]p
